[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    188[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    189[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    190[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    191[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: episode enrollment and protocol selection, longitudinal-store initialization with cross-system event subscription, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous warning-sign screening, identity-and-context loading with current-plan-state retrieval, conversation handling with protocol-grounded responses, output safety screening with scope verification, escalation routing to care managers and clinical staff when applicable, care-team reporting with structured handoff payloads, and audit logging with episode-level retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (cross-system event integration as architectural primitive, coordination-protocol-as-code with named ownership, multi-organization information bridging, episode-level tracking, and patient-as-narrator-versus-system-of-record reconciliation).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    192[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    193[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    194[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── EPISODE ENROLLMENT + PROTOCOL SELECTION ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trigger sources]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Discharge from inpatient stay                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Placement of a complex referral                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Initiation of a high-risk care plan                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team manual enrollment                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient self-enrollment                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Episode classification]                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Map the trigger to a coordination protocol type      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (post-discharge cardiac, post-discharge orthopedic,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      oncology induction, transplant maintenance,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      transition between insurance plans, others)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each protocol has structured definition: events that │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      should happen, timing windows, touchpoints, warning  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      signs, escalation criteria, off-boarding criteria    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Consent posture]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent for coordination-assistant        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      interaction with reviewed language                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Explicit non-clinician disclosure acknowledged       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel preferences captured                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-organization information-sharing consent       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      collected separately and revocable                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-information-sharing consent collected      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      separately                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: enrolled patient with active protocol; signed  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    consent record; longitudinal store initialized]        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE + EVENT SUBSCRIPTION ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-episode longitudinal store]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care-episode protocol with version            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plan items (referrals, appointments,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      prescriptions, labs, imaging, follow-ups)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active providers across organizations                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode start, expected end, current status          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Warning-sign list specific to episode                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation criteria specific to episode              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Cross-system event subscription]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral system: referral placed, scheduled,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      completed, declined                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduling system: appointment scheduled, kept,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      missed, cancelled, rescheduled                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR: encounters, problem-list updates, medication-   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      list updates, lab orders, lab results, imaging       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      orders, imaging results, discharge summaries from    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      external facilities (where exchange permits)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Claims data (where consented and integrated):        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      encounter notifications, external-facility events    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy: prescriptions filled, prior authorizations,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      refills due, refills missed                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Labs: orders placed, samples collected, results      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      returned, abnormal flags                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Biometric devices (where consented and integrated):  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      readings within thresholds, readings outside         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      thresholds                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management platform: tasks, alerts, notes       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Missing-event detection]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-protocol expected timeline                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-event tolerance windows                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-missing-event escalation cadence                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready; event-driven        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    triggering active]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, protocol-driven]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Day-2 post-discharge wellness check                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Day-7 progress check                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-appointment preparation                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-appointment follow-up                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prescription-refill nudge                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Missing-action escalation                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Warning-sign monitoring touchpoint                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, event-driven]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral placed: prepare patient for what to expect  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment scheduled: confirm patient awareness     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment missed: ask about barrier                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prescription not filled: ask about pharmacy issue    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Lab result returned (and abnormal flag): handoff     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      to clinical team and patient-prep talking points     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - External hospitalization: transition coordination    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I am a coordination assistant from your care team," │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      not a doctor or care manager                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I can help with appointments, prescriptions,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      questions about your plan, and connecting you with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the right people"                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm not able to provide diagnosis or clinical       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      advice; for those, I will connect you with your      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      care team"                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If this is an emergency, call 911"                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
