[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated bot responses                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active protocol version                              │
