[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Episode-level retention discipline]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to longest of HIPAA's six-year       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, state-specific medical-record retention,    │
