[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      hold obligations                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    569[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as multi-quarter commitment]       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    570[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode-type, per-cohort tracking                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    571[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Readmission rates, ED-visit rates, gap-closure       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    572[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      rates, time-to-resolution, patient-reported          │
